程序包 sample

This is the package for main game body Basic model of the pacman game is set up with in this class for performing its functionality.

请参阅: 说明

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    BarObstacle
    This class BarObstacle defines a bar obstacle appears in the game board Provided by Color, Rectangle
    Class BarObstacle could define an instance of obstacle bar from a rectangle as the template.
    Cookie
    Class Cookie describes the implementation of a single cookie in the game Provided by Color, Circle
    This class describes the implementation of a single cookie in the game.
    GameManager
    This class GameManager enables the interactions among all elements in pacman.
    Ghost
    Class Ghost represent the template of a ghost in pacman game Provided by AnimationTimer, Image, ImageView, Color, Rectangle, Random, Runnable.
    Main  
    Pacman
    Class Pacman is the class defining a pacman in the game page.
    Round
    Class Round defines a basic data structure for a ScoreBoard to pop up at the end of each round.
    Score
    Class Score defines the score board shown when the game is in progress Provided by Group, Color, Font, Text.
    ScoreBoard
    Class ScoreBoard represents the permanent high score list appears at the end of each round.
    SetUp
    Class SetUp is the integration class for all customizations.

程序包sample的说明

This is the package for main game body

Basic model of the pacman game is set up with in this class for performing its functionality.
Main model included:
in-game board
pacman
ghost
result board


Author: Boon Giin Lee
Heng Yu
Chen Liao


version: 1.0.3
